Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) in Computer Vision tasks, specifically in learning topological and relational properties and invariance to non-linear distortions. This suggests that the paper belongs to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a new loss function for CNN models, which falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the embedding of neural networks, which falls under the sub-categories of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Multimedia (cs.MM).
